            <li><strong>Paid post (paid media)</strong> — public kanallarda yopiq kontentga kirish uchun to'lov.</li>
            <li><strong>Paid reactions</strong> — postga "yulduz" reaktsiyasi qo'yish (har bittasi 1 Star).</li>
